<HEADLINE> Commonwealth Chief Calls for Consensus in Nigeria </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 8 (Xinhua) -- Commonwealth Secretary General Chief
Emeka Anyaoku Monday appealed to all Nigerians to reach a genuine
national consensus following the death of General Sani Abacha.
</P>
<P>
