As SPDB's first branch in southwest China, the Chongqing branch
aims to promote economic co-operation between Shanghai and
Chongqing and the overall development of the Yangtze River
Economic Zone.
</P>
<P>
At the opening ceremony, the SPDB lent a 55-million-yuan loan
to a major project of Chongqing city and donated 200,000 yuan to
the construction of a Hope Project primary school. 
