his belief that the visit will help advance Sino-Italian relations
to a new phase.
</P>
<P>
Both countries feature splendid civilizations, and their
people have long-cherished friendship, Zhu said.
</P>
<P>
Cooperation between the two countries has developed rapidly
since establishment of Sino-Italian diplomatic relations, Zhu said.
</P>
<P>
