President Scalfaro said he is delighted that China is playing
a more active role in international affairs.
</P>
<P>
Scalfaro strongly suggested that the bilateral traditional
relationship as well as cooperation be further developed between
Italy and China.
</P>
<P>
Both sides also conferred on issues of common concern during
the meeting.  
