Jurship topped the gainers list of the day as it rose by 45
cents to finish at 8 Singapore dollars. Kepfels increased by 34
cents to end at 4.46 Singapore dollars. TLB Land was up by 22
cents to close at 1.2 Singapore dollars.
</P>
