Steering Committee on Healthy Living on May 27 and before the
launching of a three-year campaign on "Healthy Living Into the
21st Century" on June 20 and a major seminar on private building
management on June 27.
</P>
<P>
There are a total of 18 Provisional District Boards across Hong
Kong and they advise the government on matters affecting the
interests or well-being of the people living and working in the
districts. 
