<HEADLINE> Chinese, Italian Presidents (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Scalfaro said that Italy places a great deal of importance on
its ties with China and that his visit is mainly intended to
increase friendship and cooperation between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
He said that there have been frequent exchanges of high-ranking
visits between Italy and China and bilateral cooperation has been
promoted in recent years and that Italy is willing to work with
China to carry bilateral relations into the future.
</P>
<P>
Scalfaro said that the world is moving towards
multi-polarization and that a multi-polarized world will be better
for world peace and that Italy is willing to see China playing an
important role in international affairs.
</P>
<P>
