<HEADLINE> Eastern Chinese Province Developing Cement Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, June 9 (Xinhua) -- East China's Anhui Province has
decided to accelerate cement production for economic growth.
</P>
<P>
