<HEADLINE> Construction of New Expressway in East China Starts </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, June 9 (Xinhua) -- Construction of the Huaijiang
Expressway that will cross the northern part of east China's
Jiangsu Province started recently.
</P>
